Class main.SickCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Cell
      • main.SickCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    main.Locatable

    public class main.SickCell
extends main.Cell
    main.SickCell is child class (extends) main.Cell abstract class. The cells are infected and produce viruses. These Cells Help the main player. They start at an initial health of -100, and when attacked by white cells their health slowly increases, and when it becomes high enough it is removed and a red cell is added when it dies.
